author: @carolfaye8557
text: â€‹@@betzyshibu6912 No, it's just a set. Jimin as well as RM, each bought apartments in the same complex that Hybe had their expensive dorm in. During the video Life Goes On many pictures were taken there. When they've all sitting around on the sofa and floor, in the background you can see a crystal chandelier which was their kitchen area. Their 2022 Festa dinner was filmed there. It has great security, a club and restaurant, etc. on the grounds. Many idols, actors and government officials have apartments there as well. If you watch "a day in the life", RM gives you a tour of his apartment as well as what a typical day is like for him. Getting up, brushing his teeth, riding his bike to work, his office and working on music, even having dinner at his apartment with a friend. The members have become very open with sharing their personal lives with us. I hope you watch all the Lives on Weverse ( they've been changed from Vlives to Lives). Jungkook has always had trouble sleeping so as of February 1, he's been doing them from his apartment during the night. If you want to know what they're feeling about their current situations you must watch them. JK has done sooo many and with JHope you can tell what he's really feeling instead of what he tells us in public. Jimin does his from work and builds projects for us. He made an Asian house from wood including the landscape and a tree. On Valentine's Day he made us a Teddy Bear with 3hearts and a secret message in the base all from a Lego kit. Sorry I wrote so much but I assumed that if you questioned if this was Jimin's house that you haven't seen everything that's going on. I'm sure you'll  love all Lives. Enjoy!
